    "Explain what the AI capability comprises, and how the specific AI element will function?",
    "• Development inputs: What is the composition of the AI functionality?",
    "Explain the complexity and structure of the algorithms, and interlinked hardware that constitute the AI functionality • Human-Machine Interaction: How does the AI capability (and more specifically the AI functionality) interact with the human operators across the spectrum of human involvement?",
    "• AI Use Inputs: Identify the foreseeable inputs for the AI capability to operate when in use.",
    "Input is the data that is required for the AI functionality to operate • AI Use Outputs: Identify the foreseeable outputs from the AI capability."
